            "description": "Upload media files (images, audio). Returns media IDs to use in practice set creation.\n\nResponse:\n```json\n{\n  \"media\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"media_abc123\",\n      \"filename\": \"diagram.jpg\",\n      \"category\": \"images\",\n      \"url\": \"https://s3.../media_abc123.jpg\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nCopy the media IDs and use them in the practice set requests."
