es; breaks down waste materials\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"first\": {\n        \"text\": \"Cell Membrane\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      },\n      \"second\": {\n        \"text\": \"Selectively permeable barrier controlling what enters/exits cell\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"first\": {\n        \"text\": \"Cytoplasm\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      },\n      \"second\": {\n        \"text\": \"Gel-like substance containing organelles and facilitating metabolism\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"first\": {\n        \"text\": \"Vacuole\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      },\n      \"second\": {\n        \"text\": \"Storage organelle for water, nutrients, and waste in plant cells\",\n        \"media\": [\"68fd7c9f117e7c21ed258f86\"]\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"setId\": \"{{match_set_id}}\"\n}"
